<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title><%='Syntuition.org â”‚ Home where intuition is synthesized!'%></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Actor|Alef|Arima+Madurai|Charm|Cookie|Cormorant+Upright|Farsan|Italianno|Maitree|Marmelad|Montez|Niconne|Petit+Formal+Script|Philosopher|Playball|Rochester|Rosarivo|Rouge+Script|Tangerine&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class=w3-row>
  <h2 class="w3-center w3-arima"><%='THEY MAKE THE POSSIBILITIES ENDLESS' %></h2>
  <div class="w3-container">
    <div class="w3-half" >
      <h2 class="w3-arima"><%='Computer Programming Languages' %></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-half">
      <p class="w3-relativity "  style="font-size: 14px;"><%='Syntuition\'s website is a combination of many computer programming languages,
       the first common language is'%> <%=link_to 'ruby', 'https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/',:class=>'w3-text-red' %><%=' which encompasses 70 percent of the website while other languages have been categorised in remaining
       the 30 percent. The languages presented here are the ones available when applying for '%> <%=link_to 'website development', {:controller => 'confidential', :action => 'websitedev'},:class=>'w3-text-teal' %><%= ' in project\'s tab therefore, it
is up to the newbie to know his/her accustomed programming language and where to apply it. For CSS framework the website is currently running on
W3.CSS from '%><%=link_to 'w3schools', 'http://www.w3schools.com',:class=>'w3-text-green' %> <%='however, it will soon start running on '%><%=link_to 'foundation 6', 'https://foundation.zurb.com',:class=>'w3-text-brown' %><%=' or'%>
        <%=link_to 'bootstrap', 'https://getbootstrap.com',:class=>'w3-text-purple' %>
        <%='depending on the communities choice.' %> </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="w3-row">
  <div class="w3-container">
    <h2 class="w3-center w3-arima"><%='Software we normally use' %></h2>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center w3-blue w3-card " style="margin-right:5px;">
        <span class="w3-text-orange w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-white w3-arima">
          <%=link_to 'Blender','http://www.blender.org',:class =>'w3-text-orange w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-cyan', :style=>'text-decoration:none;' %></span><br>
        <span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;"><%=image_tag 'blender3d.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Blender 3D software' %>
          <%='Blender is used for projects like 3D animations, SkyLab and others.'%></span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center w3-card w3-brown" style="margin-right:5px;">
        <span class="w3-relativity" >
          <span class="w3-text-blue w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-red w3-arima">
          <%= link_to 'Synfig','https://www.synfig.org',:class=>'w3-text-blue w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-red',:style=>'text-decoration: none;' %></span> <%='and'%>
          <span class="w3-text-orange w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-teal w3-arima">
            <%=link_to 'Harmony', 'https://www.toonboom.com',:class=>'w3-text-orange w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-white',:style=>'text-decoration:none;' %></span>
        </span><br/><span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;">
        <%=image_tag 'harmony.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Toon Boom Harmony and Synfig' %>
        <%='Synfig and Harmony are used for making 2D animations.' %></span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center w3-card w3-green" style="margin-right:5px;">
        <span class="w3-text-black w3-arima w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-yellow">
          <%=link_to 'Three.js', 'https://threejs.org/',:class=>"w3-text-black w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-cyan",:style=>'text-decoration: none;' %></span><br/>
        <span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;"><%=image_tag 'threejs.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Threejs' %><%='Threejs is mainly used for putting New 3D art on our web engine.'%></span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center w3-card w3-grey" style="margin-right:5px;">
        <span class="w3-text-white w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-amber w3-arima"><%=link_to 'Medibang/Clip', 'https://www.clipstudio.net/en',:class=>'w3-text-blue w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-amber',:style=>'text-decoration: none;' %></span><br/>
        <span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;"><%=image_tag 'medibang.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Medibang and clip paint studio' %><%='Both clip studio and medibang are used for making comics.' %></span></p>

    </div>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center  w3-card w3-black" style="margin-right:5px;"><span class="w3-text-lime w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-teal w3-arima"><%=link_to 'Crazy Bump', 'http://www.crazybump.com',:class=>'w3-text-purple w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-teal',:style=>'text-decoration: none;' %></span><br>
        <span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;"><%=image_tag 'crazy4bump.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Crazy4bump' %><%='We use this tool to create different forms of textures.'%> </span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col m2">
      <p class="w3-center  w3-card w3-teal" style="margin-right:5px;"><span class="w3-text-white w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-aqua w3-arima" >
        <%=link_to 'Godot', 'https://godotengine.org/',:class=>'w3-text-blue w3-xlarge w3-hover-text-aqua',:style=>'text-decoration: none;' %></span><br>
        <span class="w3-relativity" style="font-size: 14px;">
        <%=image_tag 'godot.png',:class=>'w3-image',:alt => 'Godot' %><%='Godot is a used for developing SkyLab.'%></span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class=w3-row>
  <div class="w3-container">
    <div class="w3-half w3-right" >
      <h2 class="w3-center w3-arima " ><%='Show reel' %></h2>


    </div>
    <div class="w3-half w3-left">
      <p class="w3-relativity " style="font-size: 14px;"><%='Show reel is a collection of advancements
        made in each month in a particular project of a year at Syntuition organization. A
        show reel is composed of animations, newly added Skylab experiments,
        modifications made in Spooky, textures add to the database,
        comics developed and many more. Reels also play an important
        role in the initial openings of the showcasing day at Syntuition.
        It is agreed that the length of the reel is ought not to exceed the 5 minutes with
        this, minor advancements are cherry-picked by debating at what should be put in a reel.
        The reels are not only made accessible to the website but also to everyone including popular
        networks like '%><%= link_to 'facebook','http://www.facebook.com',:class=>'w3-text-blue' %>
        <%=link_to 'youtube','http://www.youtube.com',:class=>'w3-text-red'  %>
        <%= 'and' %> <%=link_to 'instagram','http://www.instagram.com',:class=> 'w3-text-brown'  %><%=' as a result,
        we recommend you to join us today.'%> </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

